### Métodos útiles de `CrudRepository`
| Método | Acción |
|--------|--------|
| `findAll()` | SELECT * |
| `findById(id)` | SELECT WHERE id = ? → `Optional<T>` |
| `save(entity)` | INSERT o UPDATE |
| `deleteById(id)` | DELETE |
| `existsById(id)` | ¿Existe? |

### `application.properties` (MySQL)
```properties
