## 10. Tests (UNSC — `@WebMvcTest`)

```java
@WebMvcTest(ControllerLogin.class)  // solo ese controller
class ControllerLoginTest {
    @Autowired
    private MockMvc mockMvc;

    @Test
    void loginValidoRedirige() throws Exception {
        mockMvc.perform(get("/login")
                .param("nombre", "Fernando")
                .param("contraseña", "1234"))
            .andExpect(status().is3xxRedirection())
            .andExpect(redirectedUrl("/credenciales"));
    }
}
```

| Matcher | Qué comprueba |
|---------|----------------|
| `status().isOk()` | 200 |
| `status().is3xxRedirection()` | 302/303 |
| `redirectedUrl("/ruta")` | A dónde redirige |
| `view().name("login")` | Qué plantilla renderiza |
| `model().attribute("usuarios", hasSize(3))` | Atributos del Model |

